                    <path d="M10 6L8 8" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path>
                  </g>
                </svg>
                Our mission
              </p>
              <p class="text-heading leading-none text-black">Making software better for everyone</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="sm:px-6 lg:px-0">
            <div class="relative px-6 sm:mx-auto sm:max-w-2xl sm:rounded-3xl sm:pl-0 sm:pr-0 lg:mx-0 lg:max-w-none">
              <div class="relative mx-auto w-full sm:mx-0">
                <p class="text-subheading flex items-start">
                  We are a software agency founded in 2011 (kolosek.com). We build so many awesome tools using Pivotal Tracker. We didn't want this to change.
                  <br><br>
                  LiteTracker is our latest release as a project management tool intended to incorporate the features that teams have traditionally loved in PivotalTracker. Having been using PivotalTracker for about 15 years, we really know our way around agile project tracking and created LiteTracker as a means to enhance and streamline this very experience.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

