          <%#= phrase('litetracker_about-bootstrapped-business-header') %>
          Backed by the experience
        </h3>
        <p class="text-base font-normal text-gray-500 sm:text-lg/8">
          <%#= phrase('litetracker_about-bootstrapped-business-subheader') %>
          We built many products in financial, medical, SaaS verticals. We’re proud to be vouch for our new product for a long run ahead of us.
