  <section id="about-founder-note" class="relative px-6 pt-14 lg:px-8">
    <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-7xl py-16 sm:py-24">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl md:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-x-36 gap-y-16 sm:gap-y-20 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:content-start">
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-10 px-6 lg:px-0">
            <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
              <p class="text-heading tracking-tight text-black">Note from the founder</p>
              <ol class="space-y-3">
                <li class="text-subheading flex items-start">
                  Over our 14 years of existence, we have collaborated with dozens of teams across various industries. During that time, we have had the opportunity to use multiple project management tools, such as Jira, RedMine, Github, Asana, Trello, and many others, including Pivotal Tracker. Pivotal Tracker was the tool of choice for several projects where we highly valued the responsiveness of the user experience.
                </li>
                <li class="text-subheading flex items-start">
                  We aimed to maintain a similar essence through its successor. Our main objectives were to achieve a responsive dashboard and a user-friendly experience. I am hopeful that we will achieve complete success. 
                </li>
                <li class="text-subheading flex items-start">
                  Together with our users, we are crafting something truly special, and I cannot wait to see what the future holds.
                </li>
              </ol>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col">
              <p class="text-black-light font-medium text-sm">Nesha Zoric</p>
              <p class="text-subheading text-sm">Founder</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="sm:px-6 lg:px-0">
            <div class="relative px-6 sm:mx-auto rounded-2xl sm:pl-0 sm:pr-0 lg:mx-0 max-w-124 ">
              <div class="relative mx-auto w-full sm:mx-0 aspect-square">
                <%= image_tag 'litetracker/founder.avif', class: "w-full h-full object-cover object-[right_center] rounded-2xl", alt: '' %>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>
